{"tid":1942165,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊 : 該立例不可多人聚集  市民出外不可多於4人聚集","createTime":"2020-03-25T01:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T05:20:10.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3eef472c900110a2481993928523b239deb01eac","tid":1942165,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:52:19.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊在電台節目表示，政府打算實行的禁酒令是「到皮不到肉」的做法。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，禁酒令的目的是要減低及杜絕公眾社交活動以及人群聚集，切斷傳染鏈，即使禁賣酒，人群亦會因為用膳而聚集，禁令又引起業界不滿，並不值得。他提出，要對症下藥，應該立例不可多人聚集，他建議市民出外不可多於4人聚集，並保持至少2米的安全距離。<br />\n<br />\n行會成員葉劉淑儀在另一個電台節目亦表示，以禁賣酒去減少社交接觸並不是最好的方法，應該是以針對聚集行為而非針對場所去推出措施。她因為之前由珠海回港，正接受家居隔離，所以無參與行會有關討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2413590/%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%3A%E7%A6%81%E9%85%92%E4%BB%A4%E4%B8%8D%E6%81%B0%E7%95%B6+%E5%80%A1%E7%AB%8B%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%9A%E9%9B%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2413590%2F%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A%253A%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%2585%2592%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2581%25B0%25E7%2595%25B6%2B%25E5%2580%25A1%25E7%25AB%258B%25E4%25BE%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%259A%25E9%259B%2586&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn2Fzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=8e21a760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2413590/%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%3A%E7%A6%81%E9%85%92%E4%BB%A4%E4%B8%8D%E6%81%B0%E7%95%B6+%E5%80%A1%E7%AB%8B%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%9A%E9%9B%86</a>"},{"pid":"f4776aff63876b56ba4fd458c44eb1ee8eee20fd","tid":1942165,"uid":55955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:55:36.000Z","msg":"咁仲駛唔駛返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a175b9de22054d4bfaf740a6a846c5f8a6f9f2e","tid":1942165,"uid":122275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cite